data.description: This 2 bed/1 bath home in Willard schools is a MUST see.  So many features  & updates throughout. Starting in the kitchen, you'll find butcher block counters, custom backsplash, gas stove & pot filler!  Head down the hall to a modern bathroom with a double sink & custom tile shower.  Outside you'll find a storage shed, 1 car covered parking & large fenced in yard.  Don't miss this adorable move-in ready home!
